平稳分布-转移概率

set.seed(1)
x_tem=500 #马尔科夫链起始点
X=NULL
n=1000 #链长
for (i in 1:n) {
x=rnorm(1, 0.5*x_tem,1) #产生下一个点
X=c(X,x)
x_tem=x
}
Y=seq(1, n)
plot(Y,X,type = "l")

trim = 500
XX = X[trim:n] #去除未收敛的点
mean(XX);var(XX);abs(var(XX)-(4/3))
## [1] -0.09194115
## [1] 1.343696
## [1] 0.01036299
hist(XX,freq = F)
d <- seq(-3,3,0.1)
lines(x=d,y=dnorm(d,0,4/3),col="blue",lwd=2,xlim=c(-4,4))

set.seed(1)
b = 1 #常数b
n_mc = 10000
alpha = function(x, y) min((1+x^2)/(1+y^2),1) #接受概率
sample = rep(NA, n_mc)
sample[1] = rnorm(1)
u = runif(n_mc) #均匀随机数用于比较
for(in_mc in 2:n_mc) {
y = rnorm(1, sample[in_mc - 1], b) #建议分布
p = (u[in_mc] < alpha(sample[in_mc - 1], y)) #判断是否转移
sample[in_mc] = (y*p + sample[in_mc - 1]*(1-p))
#转移到下一个点
}
plot(1:n_mc, sample, 'l')

hist(sample,freq = F,ylim=c(0,0.2),xlim=c(-30,10))

qqplot(sample[-1],rcauchy(in_mc-1))

set.seed(1)
b = 1 #常数b
n_mc = 10000
miu=2;sig=2
alpha = function(x, y) min(exp(y^2+x^2-2*y*miu+2*x*miu)/(2*sig^2),1) #接受概率
sample = rep(NA, n_mc)
sample[1] = rnorm(1)
u = runif(n_mc) #均匀随机数用于比较
for(in_mc in 2:n_mc) {
y = rnorm(1, sample[in_mc - 1], b) #建议分布
p = (u[in_mc] < alpha(sample[in_mc - 1], y)) #判断是否转移
sample[in_mc] = (y*p + sample[in_mc - 1]*(1-p))
#转移到下一个点
}
plot(1:n_mc, sample, 'l')

hist(sample[-c(1:1000)],freq = F)

qqplot(sample[-c(1:1000)],rnorm(in_mc-1,2,2))

set.seed(1)
f = function(theta) {
exp(-40 * (theta - 0.14) ^ 2 / 2) / (1 + theta ^ 2)
}
g = function(theta) theta * f(theta)
a = integrate(f,-Inf, Inf)$value #归一化常数
expectaion_theta = integrate(g,-Inf, Inf)$value / a #期望
#蒙特卡洛
set.seed(1); b = 1
n_mc = 40000 #链长
warmup = 30000 #舍去
alpha = function(x, y)
min(exp(-40 * (y - 0.14) ^ 2 / 2)/exp(-40 * (x - 0.14) ^ 2 / 2), 1) #接受概率
sample = rep(NA, n_mc)
sample[1] = rcauchy(1)
u = runif(n_mc)
for (in_mc in 2:n_mc) {
y = rcauchy(1) #建议分布
p = (u[in_mc] < alpha(sample[in_mc - 1], y)) #判断是否转移
sample[in_mc] =(y * p + sample[in_mc - 1] * (1 - p)) 
#转移到下一个点
}
hist(sample[warmup:n_mc],freq = F)

#对收敛链计算均值
x = sample[warmup:n_mc] 
mean(x);expectaion_theta
## [1] 0.1347971
## [1] 0.1338351
set.seed(1)
y = c(14, rep(1, 3), 5) #数据
thinning = 10
n_mc = 5000   * thinning #链长
#各参数初始点
theta = rep(NA, n_mc)
eta = rep(NA, n_mc)
z1 = rep(NA, n_mc)
z2 = rep(NA, n_mc)
theta[1] = runif(1)
eta[1] = runif(1)
z1[1] = rbinom(1, y[1], 2 * theta[1] / (2 * theta[1] + 1))
z2[1] = rbinom(1, y[4], 2 * eta[1] / (2 * eta[1] + 3))
for (in_mc in 2:n_mc) {
theta[in_mc] = rbeta(1, z1[in_mc - 1] + y[2] + 1, y[5] + 1) *
(1 - eta[in_mc - 1]) #更新theta
eta[in_mc] = rbeta(1, y[3] + z2[in_mc - 1] + 1, y[5] + 1) *
(1 - theta[in_mc]) #更新eta
z1[in_mc] = rbinom(1, y[1], 2 * theta[in_mc] /
(2 * theta[in_mc] + 1)) #更新z1
z2[in_mc] = rbinom(1, y[4], 2 * eta[in_mc] /
(2 * eta[in_mc] + 3)) #更新z2
}
idx = !as.logical((1:n_mc) %% thinning) #每10个点取子链

j=1
sample_theta = theta[idx]
sam=vector()
mea=vector()
for(i in seq(1,n_mc/10-19,by=200)){
  sam = sample_theta[i:i+199]
  mea[j] = mean(sam)
  j=j+1
}
plot(1:length(mea),mea)

sample_theta = theta[1000:n_mc];mean(sample_theta);var(sample_theta)
## [1] 0.5201072
## [1] 0.01774078
sample_eta = eta[idx]
sample_eta = eta[1000:n_mc];mean(sample_eta);var(sample_eta)
## [1] 0.1228096
## [1] 0.006567195
